{"tid":2174746,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民研增「評分量尺」林鄭負420.3分","createTime":"2020-08-26T05:37:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T05:51:51.000Z","uid":25558,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4451111c524f878ee299428f063436499f3ecb23","tid":2174746,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T05:37:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200826/JOPJS2CSVFC63KKAZAUXMLU2RQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200826%2FJOPJS2CSVFC63KKAZAUXMLU2RQ%2F&d=mfTbPTXtdXcWugdQC%2B6BDnejezXkYyU2Z26LisGJHUw%3D&h=04946870\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200826%2FJOPJS2CSVFC63KKAZAUXMLU2RQ%2F&h=e03e50dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200826/JOPJS2CSVFC63KKAZAUXMLU2RQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n民研增「評分量尺」林鄭負420.3分<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/5UIBek92znVI3l1QYmfRvzwLPlg=/809x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4OIIUXEY6VESPFQVT25AQ7TNAI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F5UIBek92znVI3l1QYmfRvzwLPlg%3D%2F809x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4OIIUXEY6VESPFQVT25AQ7TNAI.jpg&h=326b5441&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鍾劍華<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】香港民意研究所昨日公佈最新的特首和特區政府民望，林鄭月娥最新評分為26.8分，民望淨值為負46，53%受訪者給0分，民研首次加入的「特首評分負分量尺」中，三個實驗群組給予林鄭的評分均為負數，當中「-1000至+1000分」一組，林鄭獲負420.3分。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n53%人給0分<br />\n<br />\n香港民研本月17至20日以電話訪問形式，訪問1,020名18歲以上市民，調查結果顯示，林鄭最新評分為26.8分，民望淨值為負46，較半個月前明顯上升8個百分點，但仍有53%受訪者給予0分。<br />\n<br />\n首次加入的「特首評分負分量尺」中，評分區間為「-50至+50分」實驗群組中，林鄭評分為負19.1分；「-100分至+100分」則為負40.6；「-1000至+1000分」則為負420.3分，結果顯示林鄭在三組實驗組的評分對照結果相若。<br />\n<br />\n民研副行政總裁鍾劍華指，。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"56c5614b8547656ae238a54364a98ade16bdd9fa","tid":2174746,"uid":306614,"like":2,"dislik